---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="公式LINEのご案内">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl bg-[--color-line] mb-6 shadow-lg">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-10 h-10 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
          <path d="M19.365 9.863c.349 0 .63.285.63.631 0 .345-.281.63-.63.63H17.61v1.125h1.755c.349 0 .63.283.63.63 0 .344-.281.629-.63.629h-2.386c-.345 0-.627-.285-.627-.629V8.108c0-.345.282-.63.63-.63h2.386c.346 0 .627.285.627.63 0 .349-.281.63-.63.63H17.61v1.125h1.755zm-3.855 3.016c0 .27-.174.51-.432.596-.064.021-.133.031-.199.031-.211 0-.391-.09-.51-.25l-2.443-3.317v2.94c0 .344-.279.629-.631.629-.346 0-.626-.285-.626-.629V8.108c0-.27.173-.508.43-.595.06-.023.136-.033.194-.033.195 0 .375.104.495.254l2.462 3.33V8.108c0-.345.282-.63.63-.63.345 0 .63.285.63.63v4.771zm-5.741 0c0 .344-.282.629-.631.629-.345 0-.627-.285-.627-.629V8.108c0-.345.282-.63.63-.63.346 0 .628.285.628.63v4.771zm-2.466.629H4.917c-.345 0-.63-.285-.63-.629V8.108c0-.345.285-.63.63-.63.348 0 .63.285.63.63v4.141h1.756c.348 0 .629.283.629.63 0 .344-.282.629-.629.629M24 10.314C24 4.943 18.615.572 12 .572S0 4.943 0 10.314c0 4.811 4.27 8.842 10.035 9.608.391.082.923.258 1.058.59.12.301.079.766.038 1.08l-.164 1.02c-.045.301-.24 1.186 1.049.645 1.291-.539 6.916-4.078 9.436-6.975C23.176 14.393 24 12.458 24 10.314"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-900 mb-4">公式LINEで勉強会案内を受け取る</h1>
      <p class="text-brand-700 leading-relaxed text-lg">
        毎月のWEB勉強会のテーマ・開催日時、新規動画の追加情報をLINEからお届けします。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-brand-100 p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-900 mb-4">こんな方におすすめ</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-brand-700">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>訪問診療を学びたい医師・看護師・薬剤師・ケアマネ・管理栄養士</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>ごうホームクリニックと連携している、または検討している医療機関の方</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>在宅医療・地域医療の現場リアルを共有したい方</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-brand-100 p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-900 mb-4">LINE登録の手順</h2>
      <ol class="space-y-4 text-brand-700">
        <li class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 rounded-full grid place-items-center font-bold">1</span>
          <div>下記のボタンまたはQRコードからLINEを開きます</div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 rounded-full grid place-items-center font-bold">2</span>
          <div>「友だち追加」をタップ</div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 rounded-full grid place-items-center font-bold">3</span>
          <div>初回メッセージに、ご所属（任意）をお送りください</div>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <!-- TODO: LINE公式アカウントの友だち追加URLに置き換え -->
      <a
        href="https://lin.ee/yXG2xgz"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-[--color-line] text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-bold shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-105 transition-all"
      >
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M19.365 9.863c.349 0 .63.285.63.631 0 .345-.281.63-.63.63H17.61v1.125h1.755c.349 0 .63.283.63.63 0 .344-.281.629-.63.629h-2.386c-.345 0-.627-.285-.627-.629V8.108c0-.345.282-.63.63-.63h2.386c.346 0 .627.285.627.63 0 .349-.281.63-.63.63H17.61v1.125h1.755zm-3.855 3.016c0 .27-.174.51-.432.596-.064.021-.133.031-.199.031-.211 0-.391-.09-.51-.25l-2.443-3.317v2.94c0 .344-.279.629-.631.629-.346 0-.626-.285-.626-.629V8.108c0-.27.173-.508.43-.595.06-.023.136-.033.194-.033.195 0 .375.104.495.254l2.462 3.33V8.108c0-.345.282-.63.63-.63.345 0 .63.285.63.63v4.771zm-5.741 0c0 .344-.282.629-.631.629-.345 0-.627-.285-.627-.629V8.108c0-.345.282-.63.63-.63.346 0 .628.285.628.63v4.771zm-2.466.629H4.917c-.345 0-.63-.285-.63-.629V8.108c0-.345.285-.63.63-.63.348 0 .63.285.63.63v4.141h1.756c.348 0 .629.283.629.63 0 .344-.282.629-.629.629M24 10.314C24 4.943 18.615.572 12 .572S0 4.943 0 10.314c0 4.811 4.27 8.842 10.035 9.608.391.082.923.258 1.058.59.12.301.079.766.038 1.08l-.164 1.02c-.045.301-.24 1.186 1.049.645 1.291-.539 6.916-4.078 9.436-6.975C23.176 14.393 24 12.458 24 10.314"/></svg>
        友だちに追加する
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
